    <item>
      <title>中国考虑设立股票稳定基金，中国人民银行释放 1130 亿美元资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/china-to-allow-funds-brokers-to-tap-pboc-funding-to-buy-stocks-m1frm2al</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国正在考虑设立股票稳定基金，并将向陷入困境的股市提供至少 8000 亿元人民币（1130 亿美元）的初始流动性支持。内地和香港股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/china-to-allow-funds-brokers-to-tap-pboc-funding-to-buy-stocks-m1frm2al</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 01:36:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北京采取一系列措施刺激经济，铁矿石价格飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/iron-ore-spikes-as-beijing-takes-slew-of-steps-to-aid-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国宣布一系列重大措施促进增长和支撑陷入困境的房地产市场之后，铁矿石价格飙升，提振了这个世界最大进口国的需求前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/iron-ore-spikes-as-beijing-takes-slew-of-steps-to-aid-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 01:34:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员纷纷涌向股市，中国国债回吐涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/china-s-10-year-bond-yield-falls-to-2-for-first-time-on-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国央行大规模刺激计划推动看涨投资者撤出债券市场、转向股票市场之后，中国基准债券收益率从历史低点反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/china-s-10-year-bond-yield-falls-to-2-for-first-time-on-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 01:18:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
